<b><span size="large">Version 13 (2025-05-25)</span></b>

• Add pause slideshow feature to quicksettings menu.
• Show current slide index and total slides in quicksettings menu.
• Show a clean image filename in quicksettings menu.
    - Example: CoolPlace-UHD.jpg will show as Cool Place.
• Fix bug which caused the slideshow queue to not save after changes to the queue.
• Fix bug which caused a failure to detect images in slideshow directory.